msgctxt "Talk_0001"
msgid ""
"<1.so><2.te_si>Sorry, my sweet Roscoe, but I fibbed a little...\n"
"The truth is...<3.te_si>\n"
"\n"
"<4.te_si><5.so>I wanna see <6.pa>Guardians!<7.ra><8.te_si><9.se_co>Flying"
" ones<10.re_co>! <11.pa><12.se_co>Small ones<13.re_co>! "
"<14.pa><15.se_co>Ones that\n"
"walk around<16.re_co>! I wanna see all the\n"
"Guardians in all the world!!\n"
"Not the ones around here that have\n"
"rusted away, either. I wanna see\n"
"<17.te_si>fresh and lively Guardians!<18.te_si>\n"
"<19.so>If I ever do get to see them... I may just\n"
"have to leave you, my friend.\n"
"\n"
"<20.so>Oh, but don't you worry! Getting near a\n"
"Guardian is too dangerous for me. <21.se_co>Flying\n"
"ones<22.re_co>, <23.pa><24.se_co>small ones<25.re_co>, "
"<26.pa><27.se_co>ones that walk<28.re_co>...\n"
"I'm afraid seeing Guardians like that is\n"
"nothing more than a dream within a\n"
"dream for me..."
msgstr ""

